TY  - JOUR
TI  - Economic Growth under Neutral Technical Progress
AU  - Inada, Ken-ichi
AB  - [This paper studies the property of the dynamic paths of a model in which neutral technical progress in Harrod's sense exists and in which the labor efficiency of newly installed capital goods increases at an exogenously given constant rate. The relative stability of a balanced growth path is shown.]
