TY  - JOUR
TI  - Risk Aversion in the Small and in the Large
AU  - Pratt, John W.
AB  - [This paper concerns utility functions for money. A measure of risk aversion in the small, the risk premium or insurance premium for an arbitrary risk, and a natural concept of decreasing risk aversion are discussed and related to one another. Risks are also considered as a proportion of total assets.]
