TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Bias and Moment Matrix of a Mixed Regression Estimator
AU  - Nagar, A. L.
AU  - Kakwani, N. C.
AB  - [Mixed estimation, in contrast to pure estimation, in regression analysis was proposed sometime ago by Theil and Goldberger. More recently Theil has proposed an f-class of these estimates. In this paper we analyze the bias to order 1/T, T being the number of observations, and the moment matrix to order 1/T^2 of a member of the f-class.]
